    "fullName": "Wong and Law Emotional Intelligence Scale",
    "description": "WLEIS 是一份包含 16 个条目的自评量表，用于评估情绪智力的四个维度：自我情绪评估（SEA）、他人情绪评估（OEA）、情绪运用（UOE）和情绪调控（ROE）。该量表简洁可靠，广泛应用于组织行为学和心理学研究。",
    "author": "Wong & Law (2002)",
    "license": "Free for research use",
    "reference": "Wong CS, Law KS. The effects of leader and follower emotional intelligence on performance and attitude: an exploratory study. Leadersh Q. 2002;13(3):243-274.",
